nodes.bodyText: Did you mean HighHeapUsageClusterRca.class instead of HighHeapUsageOldGenRca.class?

No, I am trying to replace HighHeapUsageRca with HighHeapUsageOldGenRca because we have both young gen and old gen RCAs.Since we are adding HighHeapUsageYoungGenRca in this PR so it would be better to change the HighHeapUsageRca as well.
